---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
	title="Terms and Conditions - Attendance Tracker"
	description="The legal terms for using the Attendance Tracker platform."
>
	<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-s-md py-s-4xl md:py-s-section">
		<h1 class="display-lg mb-s-xl tracking-tighter">Terms and Conditions</h1>
		
		<div class="space-y-s-xl body-sm text-body leading-relaxed">
			<section>
				<h2 class="body-md font-semibold text-ink mb-s-sm">1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
				<p>By accessing and using Attendance Tracker, you agree to be bound by these Terms and Conditions and our Privacy Policy.</p>
			</section>

			<section>
				<h2 class="body-md font-semibold text-ink mb-s-sm">2. Use of Service</h2>
				<p>You agree to use this service for personal, non-commercial purposes. You are responsible for the accuracy of the data you enter.</p>
			</section>

			<section>
				<h2 class="body-md font-semibold text-ink mb-s-sm">3. Disclaimer</h2>
				<p>Attendance Tracker provides predictions based on the data you provide. We are not responsible for any academic consequences (e.g., being debarred from exams) resulting from inaccurate tracking or reliance on our predictions. Always cross-verify with your official college records.</p>
			</section>

			<section>
				<h2 class="body-md font-semibold text-ink mb-s-sm">4. Modifications</h2>
				<p>We reserve the right to modify or discontinue the service at any time without prior notice.</p>
			</section>

			<p class="caption text-mute mt-s-4xl">Last updated: May 30, 2026</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</Layout>
